&lt;p&gt;That would be nice and yes a patch on top of 35615 is a correct place as there is already an option to show/set quota for the pol.&lt;br/&gt;
If so, I will close this ticket - I created it mostly to don&apos;t forget about this problem.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
