&lt;p&gt;This is a fix that is not relevant except with 35615, right?&#160; If so, I think it&apos;s clearer to just put another patch associated with the original LU.&#160; If I&apos;ve misunderstood and this fix makes sense &lt;b&gt;without&lt;/b&gt; 35615, then never mind. &lt;img class=&quot;emoticon&quot; src=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/images/icons/emoticons/smile.png&quot; height=&quot;16&quot; width=&quot;16&quot; align=&quot;absmiddle&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; border=&quot;0&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
